'''颞中回'''（{{lang-en|Middle temporal gyrus}}）是[[大脑|大脑]][[颞叶|颞叶]]的一个[[脑回|脑回]]，位于[[颞下沟|颞下沟]]与[[颞上沟|颞上沟]]之间<ref>{{Cite web|title=Middle Temporal Gyrus - an overview {{!}} ScienceDirect Topics|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/middle-temporal-gyrus|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=www.sciencedirect.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Middle temporal gyrus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/middle-temporal-gyrus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-10|last=Loh|first=Daniel|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref>。结构上，[[外侧沟|外侧沟]]与[[枕前切迹|枕前切迹]]之间可划出一条虚拟连线，被视为颞中回的后部界限。

== 功能 ==
颞中回参与脑部许多不同功能，譬如思考距离、识别人脸、情感识别、阅读理解等<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Perception of Facial Expressions and Voices and of their Combination in the Human Brain|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0010945208701771|last=Pourtois|first=G|last2=Degelder|first2=B|date=2005|journal=Cortex|issue=1|doi=10.1016/S0010-9452(08)70177-1|volume=41|pages=49–59|language=en|last3=Bol|first3=A|last4=Crommelinck|first4=M}}</ref><ref name="pmid23767923">{{Cite journal|title=Stimulating the brain's language network: syntactic ambiguity resolution after TMS to the inferior frontal gyrus and middle temporal gyrus.|url=https://repository.ubn.ru.nl/bitstream/2066/116682/1/116682-OA.pdf|first1=DJ.|last2=Hagoort|first2=P.|date=Oct 2013|journal=J Cogn Neurosci|issue=10|doi=10.1162/jocn_a_00430|volume=25|pages=1664–77|pmid=23767923|last1=Acheson|hdl=2066/116682}}</ref>。左侧[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]的颞中回在人进行诗歌创作时也较为活跃<ref>Brain activity and connectivity during poetry composition: Toward a multidimensional model of the creative process Siyuan Liu, Michael G. Erkkinen, Meghan L. Healey, Yisheng Xu, Katherine E. Swett, Ho Ming Chow, Allen R. Braun</ref>。

== 临床 ==
一些研究显示，左侧大脑半球的颞中回后部损伤，可造成对于[[汉字|汉字]]的[[失讀症|失读症]]、[[失写症|失写症]]<ref name="pmid18641429">{{Cite journal|title=Agraphia for kanji resulting from a left posterior middle temporal gyrus lesion.|first1=Y.|last2=Mimura|first2=I.|journal=Behav Neurol|issue=3|doi=10.1155/2008/393912|year=2008|volume=19|pages=93–106|pmc=5452449|pmid=18641429|last3=Mannen|first3=T.|last1=Sakurai}}</ref>。

